Interface SubFlowNode

All Superinterfaces:
Node, java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
SubFlowNodeImpl
public interface SubFlowNode
extends Node

Represents a sub-flow in a RuleFlow. The node will continue if the sub-flow has ended.
